-- B y   D a v i d   M a l i n g h a   D o y a
-- 
2011-05-17T08:18:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-17/standard-bank-s-tanzania-unit-to-start-shariah-loans-news-says.html
Standard Bank Group Ltd.’s Tanzanian
unit may later this year start offering loans based on Shariah
banking rules, the  Daily News  reported, citing board member
Mohammed Issa.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
